label: uncl6155
comment: Code specifying the name of a non-discrete measurement.

values.label: Clear
values.comment: The measurement has returned a clear result.

values.label: Hazy
values.comment: The measurement has returned a hazy result.

values.label: Excess
values.comment: The measurement has returned a result which is in excess of that expected.

values.label: Some
values.comment: Some amount of the attribute being measured was found.

values.label: Undetectable
values.comment: The attribute being measured was undetectable.

values.label: Trace
values.comment: A trace of the attribute being measured was found.

values.label: Yes
values.comment: The measurement returned a yes result.

values.label: Closed
values.comment: The measurement returned a closed result.

values.label: Passed
values.comment: The measurement passed the required criteria.

values.label: Present
values.comment: The attribute being measured was present.

values.label: Gel
values.comment: Indicates that the item measured is semi-solid colloidal.

values.label: OK
values.comment: The measurement returned an OK result.

values.label: Slight
values.comment: A slight amount of the attribute being measured was found.

values.label: No Good
values.comment: The result of the measurement was no good.

values.label: Marginal
values.comment: The result of the measurement was marginal.

values.label: Nil
values.comment: No amount of the attribute being measured was found.

values.label: Positive
values.comment: A non-discrete value is positive.

values.label: Open
values.comment: The result of the measurement was open.

values.label: Free
values.comment: Indicates that the item measured unrestricted.

values.label: No
values.comment: The measurement returned a no result.

values.label: Checked
values.comment: The measurement returned a checked result.

values.label: Fail
values.comment: The measurement returned a fail result.

values.label: Absent
values.comment: The attribute being measured was absent.

values.label: Good
values.comment: The measurement returned a good result.

values.label: Fair
values.comment: The measurement returned a fair result.

values.label: Poor
values.comment: The measurement returned a poor result.

values.label: Excellent
values.comment: The measurement returned an excellent result.

values.label: Bright
values.comment: The result was intense and/or vivid.

values.label: To be determined
values.comment: The measurement is to be determined.

values.label: High
values.comment: The result of the measurement is high.

values.label: Ambient temperature
values.comment: The temperature of the surrounding area or environment.

values.label: Conditional, free
values.comment: Indicates that the item measured is conditionally unrestricted.

values.label: Balance
values.comment: The measurement is balanced.

values.label: Complete
values.comment: The measurement is complete.

values.label: Low
values.comment: The attribute being measured had a low measurement.

values.label: Not applicable
values.comment: The measurement is not applicable.

values.label: Not determined
values.comment: The measurement has not been determined.

values.label: Negligible
values.comment: A negligible amount of the attribute being measured was found.

values.label: Moderate
values.comment: A moderate amount of the attribute being measured was found.

values.label: Appreciable
values.comment: An appreciable amount of the attribute being measured was found.

values.label: Not available
values.comment: The measurement was not available.

values.label: Uncontrolled temperature
values.comment: Uncontrolled temperature conditions.

values.label: Chilled
values.comment: Kept at a low temperature without freezing.

values.label: Frozen
values.comment: Kept at a temperature below the freezing point.

values.label: Temperature controlled
values.comment: Required temperature value.

values.label: Negative
values.comment: A non-discrete value is negative.

values.label: Variable
values.comment: A non-discrete value is variable.

values.label: Partial
values.comment: A measurement that is partial.

values.label: Dry ice
values.comment: The temperature of the goods being cooled by dry ice or solid carbon dioxide.

values.label: Mutually defined
values.comment: A code assigned within a code list to be used on an interim basis and as defined among trading partners until a precise code can be assigned to the code list.
